Rattrap opens a com to kup "kup where are you?"

EmprzAnastazia@... wrote:In a message dated 6/2/03 11:29:57 PM Central Daylight Time, roborick007@... writes:


He transformes to robot mode, drawing his plasma rifle from subspace. Kup tries to remember his old identification from the era that the Ark was bult in order to shut it down.

Kup: Ark, computer interface. Identification: Autobot Military Academy Commedant, Iacon City Security Chief, Kup. Authorization security code: Kup-47-alpha-tango.

Kup hoped that his old security clearance would work and shut down the defenses.



Kup's old security code does not work. Obviously th Ark had been tampered with, mainly the security defenses. 

The 2 main turrets then picked up Kup's signature, turned with a whir, & aimed directly at the old security cooridinator. 2 shots were fired off at Kup, but were only warning shots & not meant to hit him.
